00:35:01.466 --> 00:35:02.901 align:middle line:90%
out of your life experience.

00:35:02.901 --> 00:35:04.603 align:middle line:84%
I mean there is a lot of
hypocrisy, and you say,

00:35:04.603 --> 00:35:07.673 align:middle line:84%
