pound of sirloin or a trout

00:35:13.078 --> 00:35:16.949 align:middle line:84%
or whatever and you were
essentially saying I'm not going

00:35:16.949 --> 00:35:18.283 align:middle line:90%
to do that.

00:35:18.283 --> 00:35:19.618 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going to play that game.

00:35:19.618 --> 00:35:21.486 align:middle line:84%
If I'm going to do it I'm
