00:35:21.486 --> 00:35:24.890 align:middle line:84%
and take full responsibility
for what I'm doing.

00:35:24.890 --> 00:35:29.494 align:middle line:84%
Now, the other part of
this debate comes down to--

00:35:29.494 --> 00:35:33.198 align:middle line:84%
yes, if you need to hunt and
this is part of your sustenance

00:35:33.198 --> 00:35:37.502 align:middle line:84%
and as you said when you
became a vegan, you didn't need

00:35:37.502 --> 00:35:39.371 align:middle line:90%
to eat that fish that day.

00:35:39.371 --> 00:35:44.042 align:middle line:84%
Now, how did you bridge
that gap into hunting

00:35:44.042 --> 00:35:50.015 align:middle line:84%
which is I don't need
to, but I'm going to?

00:35:50.015 --> 00:35:53.018 align:middle line:84%
What was that debate
in your mind?

00:35:53.018 --> 00:35:55.454 align:middle line:84%
>> There were a couple of
things that drew me to hunting.

00:35:55.454 --> 00:35:57.623 align:middle line:84%
One was that ethical
confrontation,

00:35:57.623 --> 00:36:00.225 align:middle line:90%
that taking responsibility.

00:36:01.793 --> 00:36:07.666 align:middle line:84%
Another was hunting as a
different way of like forestry,

00:36:07.666 --> 00:36:09.501 align:middle line:90%
a different way of interacting

00:36:09.501 --> 00:36:11.403 align:middle line:84%
with the landscape
that I live in.

00:36:11.403 --> 00:36:15.173 align:middle line:84%
I'm part of this
natural community here.

00:36:15.173 --> 00:36:21.613 align:middle line:84%
And when I started to hunt and
pay attention to animal sign,

00:36:21.613 --> 00:36:23.949 align:middle line:84%
I learned things that I
didn't learn as a hiker

00:36:23.949 --> 00:36:25.083 align:middle line:90%
or as a bird watcher

00:36:25.083 --> 00:36:27.986 align:middle line:84%
as a canoeist you know,
the things like this.

00:36:27.986 --> 00:36:31.556 align:middle line:84%
But that's central debate,
that central question

00:36:31.556 --> 00:36:34.793 align:middle line:90%
of I don't need to hunt.

00:36:34.793 --> 00:36:39.231 align:middle line:84%
I don't need to take of that
particular animal's life.

00:36:39.231 --> 00:36:42.067 align:middle line:90%
I can let that animal walk away.

00:36:42.067 --> 00:36:49.341 align:middle line:84%
That remained and it didn't
just get resolved for me,

00:36:49.341 --> 00:36:56.782 align:middle line:84%
