the kudu and then kneels

00:51:53.144 --> 00:51:59.417 align:middle line:84%
down beside it and
sprinkled sand on it,

00:51:59.417 --> 00:52:01.519 align:middle line:84%
and just like holy water,
the way he does it it's

00:52:01.519 --> 00:52:04.889 align:middle line:84%
like a priest, you know,
sprinkling holy water

00:52:04.889 --> 00:52:08.259 align:middle line:84%
and he take some saliva
from the corner of his mouth

00:52:08.259 --> 00:52:10.695 align:middle line:84%
and rubs his own legs which
are aching after eight hours

00:52:10.695 --> 00:52:13.164 align:middle line:90%
or something of running.

00:52:13.164 --> 00:52:15.132 align:middle line:84%
>> The warrior rubs--
the hunter rubs--

00:52:15.132 --> 00:52:16.267 align:middle line:90%
>> On his own legs.

00:52:16.267 --> 00:52:18.002 align:middle line:84%
>> -- his legs with the
saliva from the kudu?

00:52:18.002 --> 00:52:21.305 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, to ease the
pain and he sits there

00:52:21.305 --> 00:52:24.141 align:middle line:84%
and strokes it and, you
know, basically, it says,

00:52:24.141 --> 00:52:26.911 align:middle line:84%
a prayer of thanksgiving for
the food that will feed him,

00:52:26.911 --> 00:52:29.647 align:middle line:84%
and his family, and
his village and such.

00:52:29.647 --> 00:52:37.288 align:middle line:84%
And there was something terrible
and also beautiful about that

00:52:37.288 --> 00:52:42.426 align:middle line:84%
and it's hard to explain but it
really resonated with me in ways

00:52:42.426 --> 00:52:47.598 align:middle line:84%
that we're both sort of
heart opening and kind

00:52:47.598 --> 00:52:50.234 align:middle line:90%
of overwhelming, is awesome

00:52:50.234 --> 00:52:54.972 align:middle line:84%
in literal sense of--
the old sense of awe.

00:52:54.972 --> 00:52:59.477 align:middle line:84%
It was something that informed
the spirit of my notion

00:52:59.477 --> 00:53:02.546 align:middle line:84%
about hunting not that I'm
going to mimic the way they hunt

00:53:02.546 --> 00:53:05.283 align:middle line:84%
or their rituals per se
but the spirit of it,

00:53:05.283 --> 00:53:07.551 align:middle line:84%
something that made
a lot of sense

00:53:07.551 --> 00:53:09.053 align:middle line:84%
at a emotional or
spiritual level.

00:53:09.053 --> 00:53:11.889 align:middle line:84%
>> When there is a very
large level of investment,

00:53:11.889 --> 00:53:16.160 align:middle line:84%
and stamina, and it sounds
as though skill and heart

00:53:16.160 --> 00:53:18.329 align:middle line:90%
on behalf of the hunters.

00:53:18.329 --> 00:53:19.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:53:19.030 --> 00:53:19.697 align:middle line:90%
>> The Kalahari hunters.

00:53:19.697 --> 00:53:20.931 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:53:20.931 --> 00:53:24.235 align:middle line:84%
>> Wasn't an easy, it wasn't
an easy catch for them.

00:53:24.235 --> 00:53:25.369 align:middle line:90%
