doing the whole butchering,

00:57:04.855 --> 00:57:08.325 align:middle line:84%
the whole disassembly
of this animal

00:57:08.325 --> 00:57:11.962 align:middle line:84%
that though I wasn't looking
forward to it and it was sort

00:57:11.962 --> 00:57:17.434 align:middle line:84%
of unpleasant, it in itself
became a kind of ritual

00:57:17.434 --> 00:57:21.972 align:middle line:84%
through which I came to
a place, sort of a piece

00:57:21.972 --> 00:57:25.209 align:middle line:84%
with this is somehow
appropriate,

00:57:25.209 --> 00:57:29.480 align:middle line:84%
this is somehow fitting whether
the deer gave me permission

00:57:29.480 --> 00:57:30.714 align:middle line:90%
or not, is another question

00:57:30.714 --> 00:57:34.218 align:middle line:84%
but somehow this is an
appropriate way of me

00:57:34.218 --> 00:57:38.489 align:middle line:84%
and the deer part of
this place on the land.

00:57:39.990 --> 00:57:43.227 align:middle line:90%
>> Interesting, the whole thing.

00:57:43.227 --> 00:57:46.196 align:middle line:84%
I applaud you and
your courage to go

00:57:46.196 --> 00:57:48.299 align:middle line:84%
through that entire
journey all the way,

00:57:48.299 --> 00:57:49.466 align:middle line:90%
