emotional stamina

00:57:55.039 --> 00:57:57.374 align:middle line:84%
to see it all the way
through, and you've done that,

00:57:57.374 --> 00:57:59.143 align:middle line:84%
and you've chronicle
it beautifully.

00:57:59.143 --> 00:57:59.710 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:57:59.710 --> 00:58:00.945 align:middle line:90%
